<plot>Aspiring actor Joe McDoakes takes acting lessons by mail order recordings and lands a small part in a movie. The film's director fires Joe when he tries to do the part sounding like 'Charles Boyer' (qv) and 'Ronald Colman' (qv). Joe finally gets a job as actor 'George O'Hanlon' (qv)'s stand-in. And that's not all he gets.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?503865</url></doc>
